Thanks to all of you,
I am fully operational again, mo!

rows.label: tlk001601_09_msg0002
rows.name: Please allow me to offer you all my sincerest apologies, mo.

rows.label: tlk001601_09_msg0003
rows.name:
I caused you all a great deal of trouble
in Superbia, mo.

rows.label: tlk001601_09_msg0004
rows.name: I am truly, deeply sorry, mo.

rows.label: tlk001601_09_msg0005
rows.name:
From now on, I will do my very best to serve Masterpon
as a perfect artificial Blade, mo!
